title: Seven Alone (1974, Western) Dewey Martin, Anne Collings, Aldo Ray

sources.title: Seven Alone (1974, Western) Dewey Martin, Anne Collings, Aldo Ray
sources.description:
A frontier family crosses the U.S. by wagon train, hoping for a better life in the Oregon Territory. This is an account of their hazardous 2000 mile trek along the legendary Oregon trail in pursuit of a dream.

Original title: Seven Alone (1974) AKA: House Without Windows

This film is available with Spanish dubbed audio.  And is subtitled in many languages.


Director: Earl Bellamy
Writers: Honore Morrow, Douglas C. Stewart, Eleanor Lamb
Stars: Dewey Martin, Anne Collings, Aldo Ray
Genres:  Adventure, Family, Western       
Genres: Classics, Adventure, Family, Western
